The '''Khedive''' was the title of the ruler of [[Sluis Van/Legends|Sluis Van]], as well as the [[Sluis sector/Legends|Sluis sector]] as a whole, until at least the end of the [[Clone Wars/Legends|Clone Wars]]. [[Candobar Inglet]] was khedive for at least several years before the end of the war.

